About Project:

Project Name: Banking Facilities Calculator (EMI & SIP) Using C Language.
Author: Yogeshwar Prakash Chaudhari.
File Name: Final.c

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Introduction:
//
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
1) The Banking Facilities Calculator is a menu-driven C application designed to assist users in performing common 
  financial calculations such as EMI (Equated Monthly Installment) and SIP (Systematic Investment Plan).
2) The application supports user login, guest access, and displays all monetary values using 
   the Indian number system with commas, making the output user-friendly and realistic.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Objectives:
//
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
1) To calculate Loan EMI accurately.
2) To calculate SIP investment returns.
3) To implement user authentication.
4) To format currency values using Indian comma system.
5) To apply modular programming concepts in C.
6) To improve understanding of structures, functions, and file handling.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Conclusion:
//
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
The Banking Facilities Calculator successfully demonstrates the use of C programming concepts such as:

1) Structures
2) Functions
3) File handling
4) Mathematical calculations
5) Modular design
6) It provides a real-world financial application and serves as a strong academic project.
